# Pekiti Tirsia Kali DC/MD/VA — 10 Sacred Power Quiz

This repository hosts the **10 Sacred Power Quiz**, an interactive assessment designed to help practitioners identify which inner power is most active in their life right now. The quiz blends Filipino Martial Arts principles with somatic awareness, cyclical intelligence, and modern learning psychology.

The quiz uses:
- **20 medium‑depth questions**  
- **4 core rhythms** (A/B/C/D)  
- A mapping system that expands into **10 Sacred Powers**  
- A dual‑path interpretation: **Feminine Path** and **Masculine Path**  
- A clean, single‑page interface where the quiz disappears and results appear dynamically  

---

## Features

- **[Dual‑Path Interpretation](guide://action?prefill=Tell%20me%20more%20about%3A%20Dual%E2%80%91Path%20Interpretation)**  
  Users choose the Feminine or Masculine Path, allowing results to match their energetic orientation rather than gender identity.

- **[10 Sacred Powers](guide://action?prefill=Tell%20me%20more%20about%3A%2010%20Sacred%20Powers)**  
  Each result includes a Primary Power, Emerging Power, Shadow Power, and Support Power.

- **[20‑Question Assessment](guide://action?prefill=Tell%20me%20more%20about%3A%2020%E2%80%91Question%20Assessment)**  
  Short enough to stay engaging, deep enough to be accurate.

- **[Single‑Page Dynamic Experience](guide://action?prefill=Tell%20me%20more%20about%3A%20Single%E2%80%91Page%20Dynamic%20Experience)**  
  The quiz hides itself and reveals results without reloading the page.

- **[Accessible Language](guide://action?prefill=Tell%20me%20more%20about%3A%20Accessible%20Language)**  
  Brief explanations are included for terms like intuition, co‑regulation, boundaries, and emotional processing.

- **[Dark Theme Design](guide://action?prefill=Tell%20me%20more%20about%3A%20Dark%20Theme%20Design)**  
  Black background, white text, and dark‑orange lineage accents for a clean, modern look.

